      "text": "correct. So that's what our I does when you when you update daily um on your google business profile, which most don't just because of the time that it takes when you update daily with unique posting, google, moves it up, that's what they're looking for. Um That we've found we've seen we've seen search results improve uh with our partners that we've rolled this out to tremendously um where they're being seen where they're being found. Um So it's it's through that organic posting and unique content."
