      "order_number": 44,
      "text": "Uh Yeah I don't work for google so I don't move it, we just know that with um by boosting your brand, um We're gonna increase your google exposure, your exposure um with daily automated posts. So just to give you um I got some numbers In within thirty to ninety days with some of our partners, they saw five, almost a 600% increase in their map views um Which and then also 369% increase in their Google My business exposure. So that's including their search and map views"
